<%- include('partials/header') %>

<main class="container nav-adjust">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h1>Elevate your Customer Conversations.</h1>
      <p>
        ReplyBot is a support response management system designed to help
        customer service representatives respond faster, stay consistent, and
        deliver exceptional service.
      </p>
      <a class="link-btn" href="/dashboard"> Get Started </a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-image">
      <img src="images/individual-support.jpg" alt="" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container article-container">
    <div class="article">
      <h1>What Is ReplyBot?</h1>
      <p>
        ReplyBot is a dynamic support response system built to assist customer
        service agents during live chats, phone calls, and email conversations.
        It provides categorized, reusable response templates that help agents
        communicate clearly, professionally, and consistently. Instead of typing
        repetitive messages or searching through notes, agents can quickly
        access pre-written responses organized by category — such as
        introductions, empathy statements, follow-ups, and closing messages.
        ReplyBot also includes a ticket workflow system that allows users to
        submit requests, track their status, and view response history in real
        time.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="article">
      <h1>How It Improves Customer Service</h1>
      <p>
        Great customer service depends on clarity, empathy, and consistency.
        ReplyBot helps improve service by:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Reducing response time during live interactions</li>
        <li>Maintaining a professional and consistent tone</li>
        <li>Providing structured empathy and follow-up messaging</li>
        <li>Tracking support requests through a multi-stage workflow</li>
        <li>Allowing team collaboration with role-based access</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        By giving agents reliable communication tools, ReplyBot helps ensure
        customers receive thoughtful and timely responses.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="article">
      <h1>Stats</h1>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

